dji.sdk.api.MainController

Class DJIMainControllerSystemState

  • java.lang.Object
    • dji.sdk.api.MainController.DJIMainControllerSystemState

  • public class DJIMainControllerSystemState
extends java.lang.Object

    Dji Mcu System State Class

    This is a base class for DJI Main Controller System State which holds the information of main controller including latitude, longitude, satellite count and so on.
    Version:
    V2.4.0
    Author:
    DJI Software
